fix(orchestrator): BENIGN continuation routes through Exit Interview (#139)
The BENIGN path (max_iterations_exceeded) was skipping Exit Interview,
going directly to facilitator. This meant router never received the
"INCOMPLETE" feedback needed to route back to project_director.

Fix: Route max_iterations through EI instead of directly to facilitator.
EI provides feedback, after_exit_interview routes to facilitator, then
router sees the feedback and continues the loop.

Flow before: PD → facilitator → router → default_responder (WRONG)
Flow after:  PD → EI → facilitator → router → PD (CORRECT)

