fix(adapter): include tool required fields in JSON schema (#136)
Root cause: The JSON schema only marked tool_name as required, so the
model was free to omit other required fields like next_specialist.
This caused Router to fail with empty args {} when parsing Route calls.

Fix: Collect required fields from each tool's Pydantic schema and
include them in the action object's required array. Now the model
MUST output all required fields or fail JSON schema validation.

Evidence from archive run_20260206_173535_96eea323.zip showed:
  tool_calls: [{"name": "Route", "args": {}, "id": "json_30f250f6"}]
where args should have contained next_specialist.

