feat(ADR-CORE-061): wire classify_interrupt into graph, remove kludge
Completes the Tiered Interrupt Architecture by wiring the new
classify_interrupt function into the LangGraph edges.

## Changes

### graph_orchestrator.py
- REMOVE the kludge intercept (lines 214-219) that redirected END→Exit Interview
- Add comment explaining the removal

### graph_builder.py
- Define terminal_specialists set (chat, default_responder, tiered_synthesizer)
- Terminal specialists: wire to check_task_completion (unchanged behavior)
