  - Exit Interview (for semantic completion)
  - Router (for continue workflow)
  - End (for terminal interrupts)
  - Facilitator (for benign interrupts)
  - Interrupt Evaluator (for pathological interrupts, when available)

## Architecture

```
Non-terminal specialist completes
    ↓
classify_interrupt (procedural, no LLM)
    ↓
├─ BENIGN (max_iterations): → Facilitator (seamless continue)
├─ TERMINAL (user_abort): → End
├─ PATHOLOGICAL (stagnation): → Interrupt Evaluator
└─ NORMAL (artifacts): → Exit Interview (semantic completion)
```

Terminal specialists (chat, default_responder, tiered_synthesizer) retain
their original behavior via check_task_completion.

