feat(research): implement Phase 2 emergent deep research with ReActMixin (ADR-CORE-029)
ProjectDirector now uses ReActMixin for internal iteration instead of
graph-level cycling. This avoids the 2-step cycle invariant that was
triggering after 3 iterations.

