  tool serialization, partial synthesis

The loop is now internal:
  Router → ProjectDirector [LLM → MCP(search) → LLM → MCP(browse) → ...] → Router

Instead of graph-level cycling:
  Router → ProjectDirector → WebSpecialist → ProjectDirector → ... (invariant)

