  - 5-phase execution: Parse → Gather Context → Generate Plan → Execute → Report
  - Per-file success/failure tracking
  - Rich artifacts: summary, details, markdown report
- app/src/specialists/schemas/_batch_ops.py (44 lines)
  - FileSortStrategy, BatchSortRequest, FileSortDecision, BatchSortPlan schemas
- app/prompts/batch_processor_prompt.md (60 lines)
