- **Error tolerance**: Halts if error rate exceeds threshold (default: 10%)
- **Hierarchical file structure**: domain/sequence_slug_hash/file.jsonl
- **Error logging**: Separate errors.jsonl per domain
- **Thinking extraction**: Supports GeminiWebUIAdapter thinking stages
